From 11544d09fe319a376af20fa77b119f9ff691bf8b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Nagarajan Maran <nmaran@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Thu, 19 Jun 2025 11:47:06 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] QSDK: wifi: ath12k: Add support to configure SLA
 parameters to drivers

Add support to configure SLA parameters from vendor nl80211 to
telemetry driver via ath12k driver.

These changes are from the below patches where the changes from last
two patches are brought in partially with respect to this configuration.
        779-ath12k-sawf-add-telemetry-configurations.patch
        861-01-wifi-ath12k-Removing-the-unassigned-identifiers.patch
        861-02-wifi-ath12k-Add-the-SDWF-functionalities-back.patch

Signed-off-by: Mahendran P <mahep@qti.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Nagarajan Maran <nmaran@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
